fira-fonts (Fira Sans & Fira Mono)

Mozilla’s Open Source Type Family

Born in 2012, Meta’s little sister Fira has grown up pretty fast. In
version 4.2 the Fira Sans Family comprises 16 weights in 4 different
styles: Roman, Roman Italic, Condensed and Condensed Italic with more
than 2600 glyphs each. Fira Mono covers almost 1500 glyphs and comes
in three weights.

Use Fira and create awesome designs!
